randomProject/
│
├── router/
│   ├── settings.py   # here we can see the dependencies
│   ├── urls.py       # here we backend logic
│
├── randomProject/
│   ├── views.py      # here we make urls after the backend logic
│
├── templates/
│   └── clock.html
│
└── manage.py

1-CREATE VIRTUAL ENVIRNOMENT
2-START THE PROJET => django-admin startproject (name of project)
3-CD clockproject => python manage.py startapp backend

final => python manage.py runserver

